<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Okay, Ive got a question and maybe some jewelers who are checking prices might be able to help me.  Why is it that now, with this last patch, the failure rate on trivials have hit the roof.  Can someone explain that to me, Im a tailor but you know how I feel.  When your stuff fails your out major plat, when my stuff fails Im out hours of hunting with no xp. so maybe we should say something</font></td></tr></table>
