<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>In response to the cost os enchanters to purchase gems and how high the cost is... yes we do usually get better prices but all prices for vendors bottom out meaning no matter how much higher your charisma gets or how much better your faction gets, you no longer get any better of a price. I pay the lowest price I have seen for gems and for plat (105pp) for the bars and I still lose money when making plat veils alot. Until you are level 40 to 45 and can go get gems off Sea Fury's you might as well plan on spending alot of money in this skill. </font></td></tr></table>
